WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.570 --> 00:00:03.224
MATT: Hello everyone, and welcome to tonight's
episode of Critical Role, where a bunch of us

00:00:03.224 --> 00:00:06.394
nerdy-ass voice actors sit around and play
Dungeons &amp; Dragons.

00:00:06.394 --> 00:00:13.868
LIAM: It's been a while! So long since Matthew
Mercer ran Dungeons &amp; Dragons!

00:00:13.868 --> 00:00:15.866
MATT: It's been a nice break.

00:00:15.866 --> 00:00:17.992
TRAVIS: That chair has been violated by more than
a few people.

00:00:17.992 --> 00:00:19.506
MATT: I can smell it.

00:00:19.506 --> 00:00:20.882
TRAVIS: They told me to wear pants.

00:00:20.882 --> 00:00:28.177
MATT: The very onion musk you got from that end of
the table. I miss it; I do! I'm excited for the

00:00:28.177 --> 00:00:32.641
new campaign and the new year. I've been working
really hard on that world. I hope you guys are

00:00:32.641 --> 00:00:36.540
excited, too. We'll have information about that
first game soon. But tonight, we're excited

00:00:36.540 --> 00:00:39.205
because we get to have the fantastic Jennifer Hale
join us!

00:00:39.205 --> 00:00:46.810
JENNIFER: I am honored and terrified. I am a
virgin.

00:00:46.810 --> 00:00:49.484
TRAVIS: A quote, right above your head, "Honored
and terrified."

00:00:49.484 --> 00:00:51.308
JENNIFER: Call me HT.

00:00:51.308 --> 00:00:57.157
MATT: There you go. Hashtag. We're happy to have
you. Excited for you to play. Once again, don't

00:00:57.157 --> 00:01:00.396
feel stressed. Ask questions if you need them.
People are here to help you. You'll be good.

00:01:00.396 --> 00:01:03.074
LAURA: Be stressed. Very, very stressed.

00:01:03.074 --> 00:01:10.031
MATT: Laura, we talked about this. Tonight, on top
of that, we have a very special one-shot. The

00:01:10.031 --> 00:01:15.762
fantastic folks at Blizzard have come together and
asked us to do a Hearthstone one-shot in

00:01:15.762 --> 00:01:22.034
celebration of the upcoming expansion, Kobolds &amp;
Catacombs. Super excited about that. For those who

00:01:22.034 --> 00:01:26.486
aren't aware of it, it's an upcoming expansion for
the card game, Hearthstone, that brings the

00:01:26.486 --> 00:01:31.219
classic fantasy dungeon crawl element to the
awesome, existing card game. It incorporates a

00:01:31.219 --> 00:01:36.298
bunch of cool, mysterious magical items, nine new
legendary weapons, some of which you'll recognize

00:01:36.298 --> 00:01:40.805
if you've played World of Warcraft in the recent
expansions. There's unidentified magical items

00:01:40.805 --> 00:01:45.129
that you can find in the game, so this has
definitely more of a D&amp;D, classic-dungeon-crawl

00:01:45.129 --> 00:01:49.291
feel. There's spell stones you have to power as
you go through. It's got a lot of really cool new

00:01:49.291 --> 00:01:53.489
mechanics that add to the game. They have a
single-player dungeon run mode now, where you're

00:01:53.489 --> 00:01:58.123
actually doing a dungeon delve with your Hearthstone
deck, playing through a storyline, making choices.

00:01:58.123 --> 00:02:03.622
It brings a whole new kind of tabletop element to
the game. I've seen a bunch of it. They even had

00:02:03.622 --> 00:02:06.836
me come and sing in the trailer, so I've been tied
to this--

00:02:06.836 --> 00:02:08.819
LAURA: It was so fabulous, Matt!

00:02:08.819 --> 00:02:14.673
MATT: Possibly other elements of the expansion.
But it's been really fun and we're excited for you

00:02:14.673 --> 00:02:18.644
guys to check it out. For those who've been
playing the game, there's a new mechanic called

00:02:18.644 --> 00:02:22.280
recruit, which allows you to recruit members to
your party, basically minions from your deck, to

00:02:22.280 --> 00:02:25.450
help you out. So there's a whole bunch of new
mechanics that work out for the new dungeon-run

00:02:25.450 --> 00:02:30.384
mode and other elements of the game, so definitely
look forward to checking that out. It is coming

00:02:30.384 --> 00:02:41.842
out December 7th, so right around the corner. Keep
an eye out for that. Go to bit.ly/crhearth to stay

00:02:41.842 --> 00:02:47.878
up to date and learn more. Also, to celebrate the
release of Hearthstone, the people at Blizzard

00:02:47.878 --> 00:02:54.401
have created a custom kobold escape room, based on
one of the lairs in the world. They'll be

00:02:54.401 --> 00:02:59.110
live-streaming players and personalities from the
Hearthstone community going through that escape

00:02:59.110 --> 00:03:06.613
room on December 5th, at 4:30pm Pacific time, at
twitch.tv/playhearthstone, or

00:03:06.613 --> 00:03:12.215
youtube.com/hearthstone. Check it out to get to
vote on items to try and make their way through

00:03:12.215 --> 00:03:16.143
it. It's actually a community-interactive event.
Looks to be pretty cool, so definitely go check

00:03:16.143 --> 00:03:19.408
that out on December 5th. And then the expansion
on December 7th!

00:03:19.408 --> 00:03:23.664
TALIESIN: This is why I feel bad in not reading
the announcements, now. That sounds like fun!

00:03:23.664 --> 00:03:30.379
