00:10:28.581 --> 00:10:36.956
Sargeras, have assaulted Azeroth. The greatest
heroes of both the Alliance and the Horde have

00:10:36.956 --> 00:10:42.711
gathered their resources to combat this
apocalyptic scourge. Traveling off to the Broken

00:10:42.711 --> 00:10:49.684
Isles and to Argus beyond to fight for the
salvation of Azeroth, these heroes will be the

00:10:49.684 --> 00:10:55.192
stuff of legend. While they're away, things are a
little slow down here in the Eastern Kingdoms for

00:10:55.192 --> 00:11:06.347
you guys, as a band of friends seeking to make a
name for yourselves. The streets of Ironforge grow

00:11:06.347 --> 00:11:12.010
dull with fetch quests and baking runs. Gilneas'
biggest torment is a terrible flea infestation.

00:11:12.010 --> 00:11:17.323
After Stormwind holds a pet-racing contest, which
you each individually lose, you gather your

00:11:17.323 --> 00:11:23.701
frustration and head east in search of real
adventure, trudging through a mire of

00:11:23.701 --> 00:11:29.161
uninteresting quests and aid to local farm-hands
and wandering merchants. You've all amassed some

00:11:29.161 --> 00:11:34.688
equipment to aid you for the new challenges ahead.
